break-word !important;\">你，看到过自己的内心吗？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那些转瞬即逝的风景，</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那些过目就忘的感觉，</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那些自以为会念念不忘的人和物，最终都变成了一片黑白。周末，抛开繁琐，来到雅室，拿起画笔，在宣纸上专注涂抹。随着色彩的慢慢呈现，心情也随之改变。忧愁挥笔而去，愉悦渗透宣纸，蔓延开来……</p></section></section></fieldset><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://123.57.218.131/Image//Image/upload/image/20150814/1439520785614022691.jpg\" title=\"1439520785614022691.jpg\" alt=\"1439520785614022691.jpg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\"/></p><p><br/></p><fieldset class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin: auto; width:100%; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-width: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section tn-page-editable=\"bdc0\" tn-page-editable-type=\"border-color\" tn-border-color=\"eo.borderColor || theme.borderColor\" ng-click=\"onClick($event)\" class=\"tn-page-border-color ng-scope tn-page-editable\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px; max-width: 100%; border: 3px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section tn-page-editable=\"richtext0\" placeholder=\"{ 点击编辑 }\" ng-model=\"eo.text\" tn-edit-html-content=\"true\" class=\"tn-rich-text-content n