ush\" style=\"margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 3px; text-align: center; line-height: 36px; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 124, 135); border-bottom-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: rgb(255, 159, 168);\" data-brushtype=\"text\" data-bcless=\"darken\">Day 6（将军柔术馆）</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">体会过书的乐趣，接下来就带着孩子进入武术的世界吧。不仅能强身健体，还可以保护自己哦~巴西柔术，孩子绝对会喜欢的一次免费体验。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://www.cddayuanzi.com:9002/upload/image/20151005/1444014512979058050.png\" data-w=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6237623762376238\" data-type=\"png\" data-s=\"300,640\"/><br/></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">内容：免费巴西柔术体验</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">地址：武侯区科华北路68号沸梦想家616室</span></p></section></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><section class=\"article135\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"135editor\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; box-sizing: border-box;\" data-id=\"44423\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"135brush\" style=\"margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 3px; text-align: center; line-height: 36px; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 124, 135); border-bottom-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: rgb(255, 159, 168);\" data-brushtype=\"text\" data-bcless=\"darken\">Day 7（米鹿艺术）</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">7天国庆长假即将结束，是不是应该做些什么留下这珍贵