190367195090169.png\" title=\"1444190367195090169.png\" alt=\"3.png\" width=\"100%\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">这是一个比较清静的角落，来这里体味一番也是极好的。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://www.cddayuanzi.com:9002/upload/image/20151007/1444190403125009961.png\" title=\"1444190403125009961.png\" alt=\"4.png\" width=\"100%\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://www.cddayuanzi.com:9002/upload/image/20151007/1444190437796017547.png\" title=\"1444190437796017547.png\" alt=\"5.png\" width=\"100%\"/></p><p>\n	</p>','upload/image/20151008/347efd0f_4f76_4be6_aa36_59fa436c5430_00000000.jpg',16,'暂不确定','18821701770','凯德天府4楼言几又里内',30.608796,104.075902,'4','游泳',1444190480154,1,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,2),(19,0,35,3661,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,2);

